divs: Sighting Detailsin passing i saw a corpse of a hairless, dull copperish colored animal that looked like the dog-like animal videoed by state trooper shown on tv. on right side of road, intact with no obvious dismemberment or abdominal swelling (as if fresh). i saw it as clearly as possible at highway speed in closest lane. i am well versed in north american wildlife and could not place animal as a fox or coyote because of size, coat, or body type. shaven house dog maybe - pointer or setter sized.
